<div class="heroShow d-flex align-items-center" style="background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(20, 22, 39, 0.75), rgba(20, 22, 39, 0.75)), url('https://loremflickr.com/1500/800/<%= @trip.destination %>,landscape');">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Let's go to <%= @trip.destination %> !!</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container" data-controller="google_map">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="section col-8">
      <div class="puceText"></div>
      <h2>You choose to go in <%= @transport.transport_type %></h2>
      <p>Here is a overview of the trip and his impact</p>
    </div>
      <div data-controller="google-map"
          data-google-map-markers-value="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
          data-google-map-center-value="<%= @trip_center.to_json %>"
          data-google-map-bounding-value="<%= @bounding_params.to_json %>">
        <div id="map" style="height: 400px;"></div>
      </div>

    <div class="section col-8">
      <div class="puceText"></div>
      <h2>Fuel burn</h2>
      <p>Here is an estimation of burn fuel during this trip</p>
      <div class="imgsvg">
        <%= render "shared/planechartssvg" %>
      </div>
      <p>For a trip between <span class="bigtext"><%= @trip.departure %></span> and <span class="bigtext"><%= @trip.destination %></span> : </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Distance in plane is about : <%= @trip_distance.round %> km</li>
        <li>During takeoff and landing, the consumption of the device is 690 liters of kerosene.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section col-8">
      <div class="puceText"></div>
      <h2>Pourcentage target</h2>
      <p>Here is vision of percentage of loose on your COÂ² annual target.</p>
      <div class="imgsvg">
        <%= render "shared/targetchartsvg" %>
        <p>paris's Target   Marseille / Milan</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section col-8">
      <div class="puceText"></div>
      <h2>Total CO2 weight of the journey</h2>
      <p>Here is vision of the total weight.</p>

      <div class="row">
        <form action="GET" class="col-10">
          <div class="co2-form">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Class of travel" class="form-control">
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex co2-form gap-3">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Avion type" class="form-control">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Number of passengers" class="form-control">
          </div>
          <div class="co2-form">
            <input type="submit" value="Calcul my emmisions" class="form-control btn btn-primary submit-co2">
          </div>

        </form>
        <p>Your emmisions for this trips are :</p>
        <h2>0,638 <span class="smalltxt">tCO2e/passager</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="section mb-5">
        <div class="puceText"></div>
        <div class="btn btn-primary px-4">Compenser mon voyage</div>
        <div class="btn btn-outline-secondary px-4">Modifier mon moyen de transport</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
